videos.description: On 3rd down, TCU QB Shawn Robinson runs and fumbles, but it is recovered by TCU for a 29-yard gain and a 1st-and-goal.
videos.headline: TCU recovers own fumble for 29-yard gain

videos.description: Under pressure, TCU QB Shawn Robinson passes off his back foot and it's intercepted by Texas Tech Jordyn Brooks.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's interception stalls TCU's scoring drive

videos.description: QB Shawn Robinson connects with Jalen Reagor for a 20 yard touchdown to give TCU a 7-3 lead.
videos.headline: Robinson airs a 20-yard TD to Reagor

videos.description: TCU RB Sewo Olonilua fumbles the ball and it is recovered by Texas Tech's Tony Jones.
videos.headline: TCU turns it over again

videos.description: Deep in TCU territory, Texas Tech QB Jett Duffey throws an interception to TCU's Julius Lewis.
videos.headline: Texas Tech throws INT in TCU territory

videos.description: QB Jett Duffey finds a wide-open Ja'Deion High for a 62-yard touchdown to give Texas Tech a 10-7 lead.
videos.headline: Duffey launches 62-yard TD for TCU

videos.description: Shawn Robinson connects with KaVontae Turpin for a 31-Yard touchdown to put TCU back up 14-10.
videos.headline: Robinson rips 31-yard TD to Turpin

videos.description: Jett Duffey tucks it and runs for a  38- yard touchdown to put Texas Tech up 17-14  in the fourth.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Duffey erupts for a 38-yard TD
